Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:06.16,utaware def,,0,0,0,,I imagine the dungeons will seem pretty\Ncold to an elderly woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:06.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,年寄りの身にゃ\N地下牢は冷たいだろにゃもね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:09.41,utaware def,,0,0,0,,How can you people do such a thing?
